unit VSoft.AnsiConsole.Internal.Cell.Tables;

{
  Unicode East-Asian-Width W/F ranges (WIDE_RANGES) and zero-width ranges
  (ZERO_RANGES) for Unicode 15.1, ported from spectreconsole/wcwidth
  (src/Wcwidth/Tables/*.Generated.cs, method Unicode_15_1_0()).

  Each array is a sorted list of inclusive [Lo, Hi] code-point ranges. Binary
  searched by `InRange` in VSoft.AnsiConsole.Internal.Cell.pas. Code points
  inside WIDE_RANGES render as two terminal cells; inside ZERO_RANGES as
  zero cells; otherwise one.

  Not in scope for this table: grapheme-cluster segmentation (UAX #29),
  variation-selector-16 emoji presentation, or regional-indicator pairs.

  Source:   https://github.com/spectreconsole/wcwidth
  Version:  Unicode 15.1 (15.1.0)
  Imported: 2026-04-25
}

